  "title": "星尘维修区：修好飞船",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "dock",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-04.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "维修区里，星尘像金色小雨一样落下。飞船的推进器少了一块发光零件。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是星尘维修区。我们先把“修好飞船”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "repair",
          "prompt": "把会发光的零件放回推进器。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "center",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "放入蓝色零件",
              "feedback": "推进器重新转起来了！"
            },
            {
              "label": "拧紧银色螺丝",
              "feedback": "螺丝固定好了，飞船更稳了。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，放入蓝色零件让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "修好一件小事，也能让大飞船继续前进。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
